documentation.text:
@title AfriId Contract
 @notice this contract helps in the registration, storage and retrieval of digital data
@notice stores the count of digital data entries as integer

@notice mapping to store the structure data of the digital identity to the wallet address
 @dev public visibility will allow it to be displayed automatically as a getter function

registerIdentity(string,uint256,string,s.details: this function takes passed parameters from the front end, processes and stores them to the blockchain

params._dateOfBirth: date of birth in the digital data formatted as a timestamp
params._fingerprintHash: converted fingerprint received as a hash inform of a string
params._fullName: full naame in the digital data
params._phoneNumber: phone number parameter in the digital identity
params._photoDirectory: stores the directory of the uploaded image as a string

params._address: address of the mapped digital identity

returns._0: PersonalInformation returns the personal information as a struct

digitalIdentities.details: public visibility will allow it to be displayed automatically as a getter function

digitalIdentities(address).notice: mapping to store the structure data of the digital identity to the wallet address

digitalInformationCount().notice: stores the count of digital data entries as integer

registerIdentity(string,uint256,string,s.notice: takes data and save it to the blockchain

viewIdentity(address).notice: retrieves a person digital details by their addresses

userdoc.notice: this contract helps in the registration, storage and retrieval of digital data
